Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.54,0:07:13.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,-怎么了  -計劃有變\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}- What? - The plan's changed.
