Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.08,0:08:09.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們不能停下  安東尼\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}We're not stopping, Anthony.
