Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.27,0:08:16.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,將孩子們拖去不知什么鬼地方\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}to haul children to God knows where,
