Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.38,0:08:27.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沿途再有傷亡\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}from losing anyone else along the way.
