Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.49,0:08:39.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們都脫水了  困了...\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}The rest of us are dehydrated, aslee--
