Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.40,0:08:53.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還活著\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}It's still alive.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.42,0:09:06.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,讓我來\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Allow me.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.44,0:09:08.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不行  它是我的\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}No. He's mine.
