Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.72,0:09:32.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,學習  冥想  逃離他們\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Learning, meditating, escaping from them.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.82,0:09:35.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他們想從她身上得到什么\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}What do they want from her?
