Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.76,0:09:40.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他們好像認為她是神\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}I think they think she's God.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.91,0:09:42.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,很高興你來了\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}I'm glad you're here.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.63,0:09:45.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,需要有人來告訴亞蕾克西真相\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Lexi needs someone who will tell her the truth.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.41,0:09:47.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么真相\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}What truth?
