Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.97,0:09:51.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}What?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.83,0:09:55.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不不  她  她看著...\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}No. No. She's -- she looks --
