Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.73,0:10:02.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我搞不懂她急速發育的原因\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}I can't figure out her growth spurts.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.36,0:10:03.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好像完全沒規律\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}They seem totally random.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.67,0:10:05.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也不知道她以這樣莫測的成長速度\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}And I don't know how long she can last
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.31,0:10:07.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,繼續下去還能堅持多久\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}when she's aging at this unpredictable rate.
