Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.03,0:10:48.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,并努力搞清楚她生長的變動性\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}while trying to understand the volatility of her aging,
