Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.35,0:11:04.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,誰擋著你\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Who was stopping you?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.14,0:11:07.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,盧爾德嚴格下令不讓我接近她\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Lourdes put out strict orders to keep me away.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.85,0:11:10.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她說我讓亞蕾克西不高興\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}She says I upset Lexi...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.15,0:11:12.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還說我是無信仰者\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}that I'm a nonbeliever.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.78,0:11:17.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但你不是  對嗎\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}But you're not, are you?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.10,0:11:22.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,梅森先生  什么是新聯盟\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Mr. Mason, what is the New Coalition?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.85,0:11:24.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們就是  領隊\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}We are, team leader.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.55,0:11:26.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在艾士芬尼指引下光明的下一代\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}The next generation to walk the Espheni path.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.13,0:11:28.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們將拯救地球及人類\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}We will save the Earth and its people.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.35,0:11:31.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要怎么做\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}How will you do that?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.01,0:11:34.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,首先  我們要拯救自己的家人\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}First, we save our families.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.88,0:11:36.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么拯救\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}And how will you do that?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.23,0:11:37.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,找到他們  拉響警報\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}I'll find them and raise the alarm.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.40,0:11:40.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們為什么要怎么做\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}And why will we do this?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.64,0:11:42.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因為我愛他們\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Because I love them.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:43.94,0:11:46.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,說得好  梅森先生  請座吧\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Nice work, Mr. Mason. You may take your seat.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:50.46,0:11:51.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,希拉\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Sheila.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.72,0:11:54.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我想請你上前來\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}I'd now like to invite you up front.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:55.81,0:11:58.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,說得好  梅森先生  我都差點讓你騙了\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Nice work, Mr. Mason. You almost fooled me.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.28,0:12:02.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今天是個特殊的日子\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Today is a very special day.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.31,0:12:03.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,希拉要畢業了\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Sheila is graduating.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.61,0:12:05.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}{\fn方正黑体简体\fs18\b1\bord1\shad1\3c&H2F2F2F&}午餐后  老時間
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.15,0:12:07.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,希拉的父母就是所謂的"叛亂分子"\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Sheila's parents are what some call "insurgents"
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.53,0:12:08.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,或者說"恐怖分子"\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}or "terrorists."
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.24,0:12:10.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,地球上的一些成人\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Some adults on Earth
Dialogue: 0,0:12:11.23,0:12:14.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對政府和領導人過于憤世嫉俗\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}have become so cynical about governments and leaders
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.50,0:12:17.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,無法信任我們的艾士芬尼兄弟們\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}that they have a hard time trusting our Espheni brothers.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.34,0:12:22.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,希拉的父母就是反叛者的成員\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Sheila's parents are part of this web of rebellion
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.32,0:12:24.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這會引發無謂的攻擊\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}That is launching unprovoked attacks.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:26.15,0:12:29.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,幸好  我們截獲了希拉母親發的一條消息\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Luckily, we intercepted a message from Sheila's mother
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.21,0:12:31.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,問道  是否有人見過她的女兒\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Asking if anyone had seen her daughter.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.11,0:12:34.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她非常愛你\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}She really loves you.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.11,0:12:35.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也愛她\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1} I love her, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.10,0:12:35.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那么  你準備怎么做\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}So, what are you going to do? 
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.96,0:12:37.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我要找到她  拉響警報\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}I'll find her and raise the alarm.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:37.34,0:12:38.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是要在...\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}But not before...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.04,0:12:40.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她帶我回到藏身之處之后\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}She takes me back to their hiding place
Dialogue: 0,0:12:40.20,0:12:42.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這樣我們就可以拯救所有叛亂者了\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}So we can save all the insurgents.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.57,0:12:43.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,完全正確\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Exactly.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.54,0:12:45.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,愿意領我們背誦宣言嗎\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Will you lead us in the pledge?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.74,0:12:49.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,地球是天賜之福\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}The Earth is a gift.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.31,0:12:52.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,新聯盟必須和艾士芬尼兄弟們一同保護地球\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}The New Coalition must protect it with our Espheni brothers.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.34,0:12:56.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們同心協力  必將共創美好新世界\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Joined together, we will build a beautiful world.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.22,0:13:46.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你是瘋了嗎\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Are you out of your mind?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.32,0:13:48.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為什么跟著我\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Why are you following me?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.76,0:13:51.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我在找你的存貨\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}I'm here for your stash.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.83,0:13:52.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒錯\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}That's right.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.46,0:13:55.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我看見你溜到迅獵獸背后\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}I saw you slide behind the Skitters,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:55.66,0:13:57.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,吃它們吃剩的\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}lapping up their crumbs,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.61,0:14:01.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,或從無力反抗的人那里偷食物\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}stealing food from decent people who can't defend themselves.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.14,0:14:03.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我盡力獲取所需  和別人沒有分別\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}I took what I could, no different than anybody else.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.33,0:14:06.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,何況你和梅森掌管這里這么久\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Besides, you and Mason have been in charge all this time.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.82,0:14:07.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看我們成了什么樣子  \N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Look where we are.  
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.86,0:14:08.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,誰是"我們"  珀普\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Who's this "we," Pope?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.47,0:14:11.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,據我所知  你可是個非常稱職的\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}As far as I can tell, you're doing a perfectly fine job
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.82,0:14:14.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,無道德懦夫叛徒\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}of behaving like a craven, immoral turncoat
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.42,0:14:15.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,心里只有自己\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}all by yourself.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.08,0:14:18.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,把藏貨交出來\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Hand over your stash.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.08,0:14:20.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,自己來拿\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Come and get it.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:24.38,0:14:27.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,珀普  韋弗  我們知道你在下面\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Pope, weaver! yeah. We know you're down here.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.35,0:14:28.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有人跟蹤你  你...\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Somebody followed you, you...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.14,0:14:35.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看來  你們倆是一伙的\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}So, you two are working together.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.87,0:14:36.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,-不是  -不是\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}- No!  - No!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.73,0:14:40.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我知道你一直在偷東西\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Look, I know you've been stealing.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.26,0:14:41.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只是不知道你藏在哪兒了\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}I just didn't know where you kept it...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.14,0:14:44.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,現在知道了\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Till now.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:44.32,0:14:45.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我謝謝你全家\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Thanks for that, by the way.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.68,0:14:47.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,聽我說  小伙子們\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Listen, boys,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.39,0:14:50.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我和你們來這的目的一樣\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}I'm here for the same reason you are --
Dialogue: 0,0:14:50.19,0:14:52.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要找到這里藏著的食物\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}to find whatever food is hidden down here
Dialogue: 0,0:14:52.45,0:14:53.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,然后分發給大家\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}and distribute it to everybody.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:53.87,0:14:56.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,分個屁  我們餓了\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Screw that. We're hungry.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.69,0:14:58.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們要吃東西...  馬上\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}We're gonna eat... now.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:02.21,0:15:03.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你少給我動手\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Don't you do it.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:32.31,0:15:34.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,別浪費時間了  珀普  快\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Don't waste your time, Pope. Come on.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.13,0:15:34.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快走\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Come on!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.58,0:15:40.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,-丁甘  -湯姆·梅森\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}- Dingaan.  - Tom Mason.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.52,0:15:42.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,見到你很高興\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}My pleasure.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.15,0:15:43.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,謝謝你能見我\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Thanks for meeting me.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.64,0:15:47.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是短波電臺嗎\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Is that a shortwave?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.00,0:15:50.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對  而且還能用\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Yeah, man. And it works.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.17,0:15:53.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果外面還有人在聽的話\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}That is, if there's someone out there to hear it.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:54.03,0:15:54.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你可以試試看\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}You're welcome to try.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:54.92,0:15:56.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,恭敬不如從命\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}I might take you up on that.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.72,0:15:59.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哈爾說你是南非來的\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Hal tells me you're from South Africa.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:00.40,0:16:02.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Uh...yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.31,0:16:03.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,約翰內斯堡\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Johannesburg.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:05.13,0:16:06.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我失去了妻兒\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}I lost my wife and son.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:07.75,0:16:10.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,首次入侵還是壁壘落下的時候\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}In the initial invasion or when the walls came down?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:11.33,0:16:12.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,首次入侵\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Invasion.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.12,0:16:14.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,很遺憾\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}I'm sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:15.61,0:16:16.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也是\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}As am I.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.29,0:16:18.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,之后一直潛逃\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Been running ever since,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:18.50,0:16:20.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,從三所艾士芬尼監獄逃脫\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}escaping Espheni prisons -- three of them.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:20.86,0:16:23.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,里士滿  格林斯博羅  夏洛特市\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Richmond, Greensboro, Charlotte.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.38,0:16:24.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,佩服\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Impressive.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.36,0:16:26.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,黑蜂獸在我往南卡羅來納州穿越的時候\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Hornets found me crossing into South Carolina,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.97,0:16:27.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,把我抓到這里來了\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Brought me here.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.90,0:16:29.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,跟我說說越獄的事\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Tell me about the escapes.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.80,0:16:31.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,每座監獄各不相同\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Every camp is different,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.01,0:16:34.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只有一個共同之處  綠色壁壘\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}but one thing is a constant -- the Green Barrier.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.62,0:16:39.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要越過它  你需要這個\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}To go over it, you need one of these.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:52.13,0:16:53.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,法拉第屏蔽服\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}A faraday suit.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.36,0:16:58.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在翻越電網的時候  讓電流從周遭流過\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}It allows electricity to flow around me as I climb the fence.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.94,0:16:59.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你是物理學家\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}You're a physicist?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.97,0:17:01.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,電氣工人\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Electrical lineman.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:01.92,0:17:05.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我可以教你怎么制造  只要給我找到銅\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}I will teach you how to build one if you help me find copper.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:06.54,0:17:08.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒有銅  屏蔽服無法使用\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Without it, the suit won't work.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:08.31,0:17:10.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我知道有人藏了廢金屬\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}I know some guys that are hoarding some scrap metal.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:10.92,0:17:11.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可以找他們談談\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}I can talk to them.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.12,0:17:14.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,屏蔽服是很不錯  但只能一個人穿\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}The suit's great, but it's only for one person.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:14.90,0:17:16.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我要讓所有人都出來\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}We need to get everybody out.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:16.41,0:17:19.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不  我們要想辦法把電網電源關掉\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}No, we need to figure out a way to cut the power to the fence.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:20.20,0:17:21.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,黑蜂獸帶我飛入這個營地時\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}When the Hornets flew me into this camp,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:21.62,0:17:24.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我看到了一個傳感器連接一條鏈條\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}I saw a sensor and a tether coming off it.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:25.22,0:17:26.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是看不到通向哪里\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}I couldn't see where it led.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.28,0:17:30.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,-你覺得那是電源線嗎  -有可能\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}- Do you think that tether's a power cord?  - Could be.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.20,0:17:33.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果真是這樣  我還真能用上你的屏蔽服\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Well, if that's true, then maybe I could use one of your suits.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:34.09,0:17:35.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我可以翻過電網  剪斷鏈條\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}I could climb the wall, cut the tether,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:35.55,0:17:37.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,切斷電網的電源線\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}And it will bring the power to the walls down.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.69,0:17:39.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,爸爸  你不是一個人  知道嗎\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Dad, it's not all on you, remember?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:39.59,0:17:40.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有道理\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Fair enough.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:41.60,0:17:42.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們還需要想辦法\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}We still need to figure out
Dialogue: 0,0:17:42.50,0:17:44.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,能讓幾百人都出來\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}how to get hundreds of people out of here.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:45.42,0:17:47.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我可以分散迅獵獸的注意\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}I could cause a distraction, have all the Skitter guards
Dialogue: 0,0:17:47.25,0:17:49.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大家越獄的時候  讓它們跟著我走\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}follow me while everybody else escapes.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:50.65,0:17:51.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但我們還需要一個人\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}But then we'd still need someone
Dialogue: 0,0:17:51.69,0:17:53.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,穿上屏蔽服翻過電網\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}to get in the suit and climb the wall.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:54.16,0:17:54.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,簡單\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Easy.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:56.62,0:17:58.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以我們又回到先前的問題了\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}That brings us back to the missing piece of the puzzle --
Dialogue: 0,0:17:59.56,0:18:01.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,教堂周圍的迅獵獸到底在哪里\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}where the Skitters are clustered near that church.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:05.50,0:18:07.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看來答案都在那里了\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Looks like all the answers are right there.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:14.61,0:18:16.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我一個人也能對付他們\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}I could have taken those guys.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:16.13,0:18:17.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒什么比看你被揍\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Oh, there's nothing I would have liked better
Dialogue: 0,0:18:17.42,0:18:18.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,更能讓我高興的了\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}than to see you get your ass kicked.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:18.38,0:18:21.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是他們有刀  而且還以為我們是同伙\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}They had knives, and they thought that we were partners.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:21.05,0:18:22.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我可不想因為你死掉\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}I'm not getting killed for you.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:22.12,0:18:23.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,-希望他們喜歡豆子  -什么\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}- Well, I hope they like beans. - What?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:23.98,0:18:28.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我的存貨就是八罐豆子\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}My stash consisted of eight cans of beans.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:31.26,0:18:32.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你怎么不早說\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Why didn't you say that?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:32.81,0:18:35.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,總有一天我要東山再起\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Hey, man, one day, I'm gonna be back in business.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:35.25,0:18:37.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在那之前  我得保證我的名號不倒啊\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Till then, I got a reputation to uphold.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:37.77,0:18:39.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我當時都打算揍你了\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}I was ready to kick your ass back there,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.79,0:18:41.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不過我也很愿意現在動手\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}but I'm happy to do it here.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:41.17,0:18:43.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這是你今天說的最智慧的一句話\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Well, now, that's the smartest thing you have said all day.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:46.30,0:18:47.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等等\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Hold on.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:47.69,0:18:49.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么啦  你還得先睡會兒\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}What? You need to take a nap, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:49.66,0:18:51.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還是需要個熱身運動  能量飲料什么的\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}You need to stretch out, a little shot of gatorade?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:51.32,0:18:52.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,-怎么啦  -你能閉嘴嗎\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}- What? - Would you shut up?!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:54.09,0:18:55.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么聲音\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}What is that sound?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:02.07,0:19:04.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,科奇斯  我是湯姆·梅森  能聽到嗎\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Cochise, this is Tom Mason. Do you read?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:07.13,0:19:09.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,科奇斯  我是湯姆·梅森  能收到嗎\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Cochise? This is tom mason. Are you out there?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:09.40,0:19:11.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,湯姆·梅森  收到\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Tom Mason, I read you.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:11.79,0:19:12.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,能用\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}It's working!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:13.31,0:19:15.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要是我父親發現他給我的通訊器\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}My father would be surprised to find the communicator he left me
Dialogue: 0,0:19:15.98,0:19:18.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,被改裝成了更低端的設備肯定要驚訝了\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}has been retrofitted to a lesser technology.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:18.95,0:19:21.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你得與時俱進嘛  朋友\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}You got to -- you got to change with the times, my friend,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:21.24,0:19:22.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就算是倒退也沒辦法\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}even if it's backwards.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:23.07,0:19:24.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我知道這件事很危險\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}I know it's a bit of a crapshoot,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:24.65,0:19:26.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是我們需要食物和補給\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}but we're hurting for food and supplies.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:27.23,0:19:28.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我的隊伍和你們的集中營之間\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}There are substantial Espheni forces
Dialogue: 0,0:19:28.88,0:19:30.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有大量的艾士芬尼勢力\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}between my team and your camp.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:31.49,0:19:32.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還有什么新消息嗎\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}What else is new?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:32.69,0:19:34.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,說實話  很多\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}A great deal, as a matter of fact.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:34.84,0:19:36.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們確認了\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}We have confirmed that the Espheni
Dialogue: 0,0:19:37.04,0:19:39.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,艾士芬尼在建造新的能源站\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}are constructing a new power station.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:43.91,0:19:47.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是用來給以前的電力網供能的嗎\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Is this, uh, designed to power a grid like the one before?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:48.62,0:19:51.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,電力網和在我來之前你摧毀的那種\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}No. That grid, along with the Espheni jamming device
Dialogue: 0,0:19:51.92,0:19:55.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,艾士芬尼屏蔽儀都是防御措施\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}you destroyed before my arrival, were defensive measures.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:55.83,0:19:59.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,新的能源是艾士芬尼用以攻擊的\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}The new power source would allow the Espheni to go on offense.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:00.31,0:20:01.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,用以攻擊\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}On offense?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:02.42,0:20:04.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這可不像什么好事\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}That... doesn't sound very good.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:04.62,0:20:09.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這個問題到時候再說吧\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Uh, w-w-well, let's burn that bridge when we come to it.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:09.65,0:20:11.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但現在最大的問題是沒有食物\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Right now I've got some very hungry people.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:11.48,0:20:12.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,抱歉\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}I am sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:12.83,0:20:14.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,現在我沒法給你弄到食物\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}I cannot get food to you at this time.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:14.76,0:20:16.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不過如果你能逃出來\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}However, if you do manage to escape,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:17.31,0:20:19.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我倒是知道你能在哪找到食物\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}I can tell you where there is food.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:19.02,0:20:20.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那就將來再說吧\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Well, we got that to look forward to, then.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:21.10,0:20:23.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我還有個好消息告訴你\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}I do have one piece of encouraging news.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:24.59,0:20:27.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們的一架無人機發現\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}One of our recon drones observed children
Dialogue: 0,0:20:27.70,0:20:30.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有孩子被送去了南邊一個集中營\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}being transported to a camp south of here.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:30.29,0:20:32.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們認為馬特也在那里\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}We believe Matt has been taken there.
